#29203
ingkludd misshapen shelled creature~
an ingkludd~
<225>A misshapen shelled creature crawls painfully about.<0>
~
An eyeless, misshapen, shelled creature lies half-buried in the silt of the 
ocean floor, its swollen body bulging awkwardly from a shell too small to 
contain it. It seems to barely move, save for a faint regular twitching at its 
pore-like breathing opening, but the moment anything disturbs it, the ingkludd 
erupts into a piercing, bubbling shriek that carries horribly through the dark 
water.
~
