snout to heavy tail, its dark, ridged hide plated like old stone. Its eyes sit 
cold and watchful above a mouth built for crushing bone, and every slow 
movement suggests terrible strength held in patient reserve. It swims through 
the deep, dark ocean, hunting for prey.  Today might be your unlucky day.
~
