#29211
mosasaur~
a mosasaur~
<244>A vast marine reptile glides stealthily through the water.<0>
~
The mosasaur is a huge, powerfully built sea predator from a half-forgotten age, 
moving through deep water with the dreadful confidence of something that fears 
nothing. Its armoured hide, immense jaws, and crushing bite make it the terror 
of inland seas, where it is said to ram vessels below the waterline before 
devouring the survivors. Though slow and awkward on land, in the water it is a 
monstrous hunter, capable of dragging large prey down into the dark and 
swallowing it whole.
~
