deep scion~
a deep scion~
<64>A deep scion is here, all fangs, scales, and hateful intelligence.<0>
~
In its piscine form, the deep scion reveals what the sea has truly made of it: 
a powerful humanoid shape twisted with fish-like features, lamprey jaws, raking 
claws, and the cold stare of something that no longer belongs to land. You're 
told it moves with awkward heaviness out of water, but here in the depths it 
becomes swift, predatory, and horribly at home.
~
