#29214
deep scion female~
a deep scion~
<64>A female deep scion is here, all slick scales and lamprey jaws.<0>
~
In her piscine form, the deep scion reveals what the sea has made of her: a 
powerful womanly shape twisted into something fish-like, predatory, and wrong. 
Slick scales cover her body, claws rake from her hands, and her lamprey-like 
jaws open with a hunger that no longer seems human. She still carries faint 
traces of the woman she once was, but only enough to make the transformation 
feel like a cruel memory wearing a monster’s skin.
~
