The water weird emerges as an upper body of clear water, shaped like a beautiful 
female figure, while its lower half coils back as a twisting column. It is an 
elemental guardian bound to these waters, malicious according to the nature of 
the place it protects. Silent and eerily intelligent, it waits unseen until 
disturbed, then rises in a sudden liquid surge to seize, coil, and drag the 
living down.
