#29225
ashiera~
an ashiera~
<74>A stocky ashiera glides here, grey-blue ridges sweeping from his brow.<0>
~
This aquatic humanoid is short and powerful, with grey skin, small ears and 
nose, gills at the neck, and webbed fingers moving with restless precision 
through the deep water. Ridged blue-grey folds sweep back from his brow, while 
a faint chill gathers around his fingertips, hinting at the coldfire and 
