#29236
giant water spider~
a giant water spider~
<239>A large water spider crouches in the drowned canal.<0>
~
She lurks where the underwater current grows still, a huge aquatic spider with 
a swollen dark body, glassy eyes, and long hooked legs that move almost silently 
through the gloom. Fine strands of webbing drift between grates, pillars, and 
broken masonry, trembling whenever prey passes too close. Though monstrous, 
she has a cold, deliberate intelligence, waiting beneath the murk until the 
right moment to unfold from the shadows and drag the struggling victim deeper 
into her drowned lair.
~
