handsome man corpse~
The corpse is that of a handsome man, broad-shouldered and finely made, his face
now peaceful in a way his monstrous shape never was. Dark hair clings damply to 
his brow, and his skin has the pale, cold beauty of something long-rested in 
deep waters. Only faint bruising around his mouth suggests the horror that once 
moved beneath this human mask.
~

