beautiful woman corpse~
The corpse is that of a beautiful woman, elegant even in death, with sea-dark 
hair spread about her like seaweed in a current. Her features are composed and 
strangely sorrowful, as though the change back into human flesh restored some 
trace of who she had been before the deep claimed her. Her pale skin is cold and
sodden, and faint red staining marks her lips.
~

