The Deepsea Healing collection was comissioned by good Eakos canal denizens who 
rescued and tended wounded travellers, to assist in their efforts. Its floating 
stone was said to draw restorative magic from the crushing depths, while the 
greaves and shield guarded healing sleepers from prowling things in the dark 
water. After the collective's dwelling was attacked and ater abandoned, these
three relics were scattered through the canal's drowned passageways, waiting to 
aid those brave and fortunate enough to recover them successfully.
~
